    Hell Beast thought about Shockwave. Could he be trusted? Probly...after 
all he did know him from a long time ago. "Alright Shockwave. You can enter 
the Ice Cave. Ill bring down the defences when you arrive."

    Black Aracnia looked to Quickstrike. This was goodbye, at least for a 
little while. Her optics began to flood, and the cold tears ran down her 
face. 
    "Ill miss you big guy. But, youre right. Ill be fine and so will Quasar. 
I guess you had better get going then..." She paused.
    And turned and began to walk away. Then, she suddenly turned around, "And 
remember, if you as so much look at that horse I will make sure you will 
never bear offspring agian!" She joked, with a smile. 

    Ominous looked at Quasar. "Ready to cooperate, or should I show you the 
extent of the Energonian abilities?"
